<br>
Lovecraft wrote horror, science, and fantasy.  The majority of his works are under respected.  I believe this is due to the era that he wrote such novels.  In modern time he'd definetly receive more recognition for such fantastic works.  Horror novelist now make a lot of money, like those of Stephen King.  You see Lovecraft has maintained and continues to aquire new fans daily.  This is an amazing feat for someone long dead.<br>
<br>
He is brilliant, and his genius can be seen in works like Call of Cthulhu where he can create a myth that continues to affect underground movements, and even religious rites to this day.<br>
<br>
Check it out, it's definetly an insane wonder worth exploring. <br>
